	   <tr><td colspan=2>If anyone has ever played the old pencil and paper RPG's then you may remember the encumerance system. The books explain it as the items weight and size determines the encumberance. I think the same idea is used here, the more heavy AND bulky an item is the more it's stone weight is. So trying to put actual weights to the system EQ uses may be just a waste of time because they are not just using weight to determine the number they arfe using they are also using its size. <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
